column2: SELECT TOP #   lt.NAME, lt.RA as ra, lt.Dec as dec, lt.incl as incl, lt.q as q, lt.PA = PA,    n.objid, n.distance * #. as distance, log1#(n.distance * #.) as log_distance,        s.z, s.zErr,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr,   s.snMedian,      l.sigmaStars, l.sigmaStarsErr, l.chisq, l.bpt,   l.EW_Hb_#, l.EW_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Hb_#, l.Flux_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err,   l.EW_Ha_#, l.EW_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Ha_#, l.Flux_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err,      g.ra as sdss_ra, g.dec as sdss_dec, g.objID,   g.fiberMag_u, g.fiberMagErr_u, g.fiberMag_g, g.fiberMagErr_g, g.fiberMag_r, g.fiberMagErr_r,   g.fiberMag_i, g.fiberMagErr_i, g.fiberMag_z, g.fiberMagErr_z,   g.modelMag_u, g.modelMagErr_u, g.modelMag_g, g.modelMagErr_g, g.modelMag_r, g.modelMagErr_r,   g.modelMag_i, g.modelMagErr_i, g.modelMag_z, g.modelMagErr_z,   g.petroMag_u, g.petroMagErr_u, g.petroMag_g, g.petroMagErr_g, g.petroMag_r, g.petroMagErr_r,   g.petroMag_i, g.petroMagErr_i, g.petroMag_z, g.petroMagErr_z,   g.deVRad_u, g.deVRadErr_u, g.deVRad_g, g.deVRadErr_g, g.deVRad_r, g.deVRadErr_r,   g.deVRad_i, g.deVRadErr_i, g.deVRad_z, g.deVRadErr_z,   g.expRad_u, g.expRadErr_u, g.expRad_g, g.expRadErr_g, g.expRad_r, g.expRadErr_r,   g.expRad_i, g.expRadErr_i, g.expRad_z, g.expRadErr_z,   g.lnLDeV_u, g.lnLExp_u, g.lnLStar_u, g.lnLDeV_g, g.lnLExp_g, g.lnLStar_g,   g.lnLDeV_r, g.lnLExp_r, g.lnLStar_r, g.lnLDeV_i, g.lnLExp_i, g.lnLStar_i,   g.lnLDeV_z, g.lnLExp_z, g.lnLStar_z,   g.fiberMag_g - g.fiberMag_r as fiberColor_gr,   g.fiberMag_g - g.fiberMag_i as fiberColor_gi,   sqrt(square(g.fiberMagErr_g) + square(g.fiberMagErr_r)) as fiberColorErr_gr,   sqrt(square(g.fiberMagErr_g) + square(g.fiberMagErr_i)) as fiberColorErr_gi,   g.modelMag_g - g.modelMag_r as modelColor_gr,   g.modelMag_g - g.modelMag_i as modelColor_gi,   sqrt(square(g.modelMagErr_g) + square(g.modelMagErr_r)) as modelColorErr_gr,   sqrt(square(g.modelMagErr_g) + square(g.modelMagErr_i)) as modelColorErr_gi,    g.petroMag_g - g.petroMag_r as petroColor_gr,   g.petroMag_g - g.petroMag_i as petroColor_gi,   sqrt(square(g.petroMagErr_g) + square(g.petroMagErr_r)) as petroColorErr_gr,   sqrt(square(g.petroMagErr_g) + square(g.petroMagErr_i)) as petroColorErr_gi,   #. - g.deVAB_u as eps_deV_u, g.deVABErr_u as eps_deVErr_u,   #. - g.expAB_u as eps_exp_u, g.expABErr_u as eps_expErr_u,   #. - g.deVAB_g as eps_deV_g, g.deVABErr_g as eps_deVErr_g,   #. - g.expAB_g as eps_exp_g, g.expABErr_g as eps_expErr_g,   #. - g.deVAB_r as eps_deV_r, g.deVABErr_r as eps_deVErr_r,   #. - g.expAB_r as eps_exp_r, g.expABErr_r as eps_expErr_r,   #. - g.deVAB_i as eps_deV_i, g.deVABErr_i as eps_deVErr_i,   #. - g.expAB_i as eps_exp_i, g.expABErr_i as eps_expErr_i,   #. - g.deVAB_z as eps_deV_z, g.deVABErr_z as eps_deVErr_z,   #. - g.expAB_z as eps_exp_z, g.expABErr_z as eps_expErr_z,   ssp.age, ssp.age_max, ssp.age_min, ssp.logMass, ssp.logMass_err,   ssp.metallicity, ssp.metallicity_err,   ssp.tau, ssp.m2l_r, ssp.m2l_i,   sspD.age as ageD, sspD.age_max as age_maxD, sspD.age_min as age_minD,   sspD.logMass as logMassD, sspD.logMass_err as logMass_errD,   sspD.metallicity as metallicityD, sspD.metallicity_err as metallicity_errD,   sspD.tau as tauD, sspD.m2l_r as ml2_rD, sspD.m2l_i as m2l_iD    INTO mydb.LITTLE_THINGS FROM MyDB.LITTLE_THINGS_RAW AS lt CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(lt.RA, lt.Dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecObj AS s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid JOIN Galaxy as g ON n.objid=g.objid JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideNoDust as ssp ON ssp.specObjID=s.specObjID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as sspD ON sspD.specObjID=s.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid=l.specobjid
